<h2>Frequently Asked Questions</h2>

<p><strong>What fire protection services does Engg-Tech provide in Singapore?</strong><br>
Engg-Tech provides fire sprinkler system installation, fire alarm system installation, wet and dry riser systems, hose reel systems, fire hydrant systems, and FM200/Novec suppression systems for commercial, industrial and residential projects in Singapore.</p>

<p><strong>What waterproofing services does Engg-Tech offer?</strong><br>
We offer PU injection grouting, epoxy grouting, basement and retaining wall waterproofing, toilet and wet area waterproofing, concrete crack injection sealing, and lift pit waterproofing across Singapore for HDB, condo and commercial properties.</p>

<p><strong>Does Engg-Tech provide electrical and plumbing services?</strong><br>
Yes. Engg-Tech provides licensed electrical contractor services including wiring, DB board installation, fault finding and renovation electrical works, as well as plumbing services including pipe repair, replacement, toilet works and renovation plumbing for residential and commercial properties in Singapore.</p>

<p><strong>How do I get a quote for services from Engg-Tech?</strong><br>
You can request a quotation by emailing <a href="mailto:info@engg-tech.com">info@engg-tech.com</a> or by submitting an enquiry through our <a href="https://engg-tech.com/contact-us/">contact page</a>. Our team will respond within 1 business day.</p>

